      "text": "folder 48 - 041\n841\n\nHe can re-establish his church/worship hence living presence in this world, despite the evil power, the lie which pushed out the true Xtians long ago. The ultimate news is, \"He -YHWH- is alive\" - i.e. alive in this world; i.e. has been transplanted (to this world!!) He enters this world + is now already present here as he was of old - e.g. in Elijah's time. The presence (Shekhina?) has returned. \"He is alive\" does not signify \"das leblose Einsamkeit\" but Emmanuel: God with u",
